dpdk vhost-user unmap dirty_log 导致崩溃

  • 由 xiangwencheng创建, 最后修改于十一月 16, 2023

  • 1qemu多次发送VHOST_USER_SET_LOG_BASE 导致 dpdk vhost-user unmap dirty_log 导致崩溃
  • 2dpdk vhost-user unmap log_addr导致访问错误:
  • 3qemu：
  • 4多队列会多次调用vhost_net_init->vhost_dev_init→memory_listener_register (BLK没有这个问题)
  • 5四个队列会调用四次dev→log_enabled:0
  • 6两个队列调用两次：（死掉的概率较低）
  • 7feature 没变化不会重复设置，不能在set_feature里面判断调用次数
  • 8一代卡硬件热迁移 vdpa 会自己 map 一次
  • 9解决方案：

qemu多次发送VHOST_USER_SET_LOG_BASE 导致 dpdk vhost-user unmap dirty_log 导致崩溃

iperf3 打大流量的时候热迁移标记脏页挂掉了

iperf3 -u -c 192.168.80.60 -b 1500m  -t 100



热迁移死掉那个问题目前定位到qemu会发四次VHOST_USER_SET_LOG_BASE，每次dpdk vhost-user这块都会mmap一块新地址，然后unmap老地址，老地址被unmap就会导致出问题：

dpdk vhost-user unmap log_addr导致访问错误:

{

    }

    /* Refresh DIRTY_MEMORY_MIGRATION bit.  */
    memory_region_transaction_begin();
    memory_region_update_pending = true;
    memory_region_transaction_commit();
}
#define MEMORY_LISTENER_CALL_GLOBAL(_callback, _direction, _args...)    \
    do {                                                                \
        MemoryListener *_listener;                                      \
                                                                        \
        switch (_direction) {                                           \
        case Forward:                                                   \
            QTAILQ_FOREACH(_listener, &memory_listeners, link) {        \
                if (_listener->_callback) {                             \
                    _listener->_callback(_listener, ##_args);           \
                }                                                       \
            }                                                           \
            break;                                                      \
        case Reverse:                                                   \
            QTAILQ_FOREACH_REVERSE(_listener, &memory_listeners, link) { \
                if (_listener->_callback) {                             \
                    _listener->_callback(_listener, ##_args);           \
                }                                                       \
            }                                                           \
            break;                                                      \
        default:                                                        \
            abort();                                                    \
        }                                                               \
    } while (0)
static int vhost_migration_log(MemoryListener *listener, int enable)
{
    struct vhost_dev *dev = container_of(listener, struct vhost_dev,
                                         memory_listener);
    int r;
    if (!!enable == dev->log_enabled) {
        return 0;
    }
    if (!dev->started) {
        dev->log_enabled = enable;
        return 0;
    }
    if (!enable) {
        r = vhost_dev_set_log(dev, false);
        if (r < 0) {
            return r;
        }
        vhost_log_put(dev, false);
    } else {
        vhost_dev_log_resize(dev, vhost_get_log_size(dev));
        r = vhost_dev_set_log(dev, true);
        if (r < 0) {
            return r;
        }
    }
    #printf("vhost_migration_log dev->log_enabled:%d enable:%d\n", dev->log_enabled, enable);
    dev->log_enabled = enable;
    return 0;
}
//#vhost_log_global_start
static void vhost_log_global_start(MemoryListener *listener)
{
    int r;
 
    r = vhost_migration_log(listener, true);
    if (r < 0) {
        abort();
    }
}

feature 没变化不会重复设置，不能在set_feature里面判断调用次数

一代卡硬件热迁移 vdpa 会自己 map 一次

static int
agile_vdpa_set_features(int vid)
{
    uint64_t features = 0;
    struct rte_vdpa_device *vdev;
    struct internal_list *list;
    struct agile_internal *internal;
    uint64_t log_base = 0, log_size = 0;
 
    vdev = rte_vhost_get_vdpa_device(vid);
    list = find_internal_resource_by_vdev(vdev);
    if (list == NULL) {
        DRV_LOG(ERR, "Invalid vDPA device: %p", vdev);
        return -1;
    }
    internal = list->internal;
    rte_vhost_get_negotiated_features(vid, &features);
    if (!RTE_VHOST_NEED_LOG(features))
        return 0;
    rte_vhost_get_log_base(vid, &log_base, &log_size);
#rte_vfio_container_dma_map
    rte_vfio_container_dma_map(internal->vfio_container_fd,
            log_base, AGILE_LOG_BASE, log_size);
    agile_enable_logging(&internal->hw, AGILE_LOG_BASE, log_size);
    return 0;
}

解决方案：

1.在vring_relay线程一开始usleep(1000)，等listener遍历完了再执行就没问题 （sleep时间不确定，目前4队列，队列多了可能需要更长）

2.或者先map出新的地址，再unmap老地址 （需要改dpdk vhost_user代码，目前改的太简单，还是可能出现使用的时候被unmap的情况）
